<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Apr1919"><font color="red">1 April 1919</font>, <cite>Yale</cite> (JJ to Ezra Pound): [Trouser affair; JJ&apos;s ingratitude re grant] In any other country would a writer who can point to such a press be, as I am, a beggar living on charity &hellip; I have beaten them to their knees twice before and will do so again.</div>
